oon.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2012/08/spicy-noodles/?replytocom=72878#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm(\"comment-72878\", \"72878\", \"respond\", \"13143\")'>Reply</a>\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\n\t<li class=\"comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"comment-72931\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-header\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/41dc3e007986c35dc46763689fa93174?s=48&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D48&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />\t\t\t\t<cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://alannashaikh.com/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Alanna</a></cite> <span class=\"says\">says:</span>\t\t \t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-meta commentmetadata\">\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/2012/08/spicy-noodles/#comment-72931\">02.02.13 at 10:41 am</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-content\">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<p>This was fantastic! We did find the portion size a little small &#8211; I doubled it and it was just enough for three adults.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2012/08/spicy-noodles/?replytocom=72931#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm(\"comment-72931\", \"72931\", \"respond\", \"13143\")'>Reply</a>\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\n\t<li class=\"comment even thread-even depth-1\" id=\"comment-72940\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-header\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/41dc3e007986c35dc46763689fa93174?s=48&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D48&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />\t\t\t\t<cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www.blogger.com